entries.journal_entry_description: Capture or destroy the rebels shield generator.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Don't let them escape alive! Take out that shuttle.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Have the probot interface with the Rebel generator.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Since you cannot interface with the generator anymore, destroy it so the Rebels cannot use it either.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Keep the probot alive, so it can interface with the Rebels' secondary generator.
